# Anthropic API host. Anchored regex.
^api\.anthropic\.com$
# Statsig SDK is used by Claude Code for feature flags. Allow it so the CLI
# doesn't time out on startup; it's not a data exfiltration vector.
^featuregates\.org$
^api\.statsig\.com$
# --- Codex CLI (codex-vanilla arm) ---
# OpenAI public API endpoint (api-key-mode users; harmless to allow for
# ChatGPT-mode too since some Codex code paths probe it).
^api\.openai\.com$
# ChatGPT OAuth token endpoint. Codex's ChatGPT-mode credentials in
# ~/.codex/auth.json refresh against this host.
^auth\.openai\.com$
# ChatGPT-mode Codex inference backend. Strings extracted from the Codex
# binary show requests to https://chatgpt.com/backend-api/codex. Whitelist
# the apex host; tinyproxy filter matches on the Host header only.
^chatgpt\.com$
# A/B experimentation endpoint used by Codex for feature-flag fetches at
# startup. Allowed for the same reason as featuregates.org for Claude: avoids
# CLI startup timeouts, no data exfil vector.
^ab\.chatgpt\.com$
